sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Connector
    participant M as Marketplace API
    participant S as Sophos API
    participant R as Reseller
    
    Note over C,R: Approach 2 - Ad Hoc Invoices with API Details
    
    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over C,M: Prerequisites
        Note over M: Reseller/Partner ID<br/>Custom Attribute Setup
    end
    
    rect rgb(248, 255, 248)
        Note over C,S: Monthly Billing (26th) - API Calls
        C->>S: GET /accounts/v1/relationships<br/>api.central.sophos.com
        S-->>C: Partner List Response
        
        loop For Each Partner
            C->>S: GET /partner/billing/v1/usage-report<br/>api.central.sophos.com<br/>?partnerId={id}
            S-->>C: Usage Data Response
            
            C->>M: Check Partner ID exists<br/>(Custom Attribute Query)
            M-->>C: Partner Validation Result
            
            alt Partner ID exists
                C->>M: Generate Ad Hoc Invoice<br/>(Invoice API)<br/>for Reseller Company
                M-->>C: Invoice Created
                C->>M: Apply Usage Charges<br/>(Billing API)<br/>to Invoice
                M-->>C: Charges Applied
                M->>R: Send Invoice Notification
                R-->>M: Invoice Received
            else Partner ID missing
                Note over C: Skip Partner - Log Missing ID
            end
        end
    end

